hivien.net/H%C3%A0-C%E1%BA%A3nh-Minh/author-wg6EAaIQ8OL-TAAIuNs-Kg">Hà Cảnh Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tu%E1%BA%BF-y%E1%BA%BFn-h%C3%A0nh/poem-93-OV94G2z33TdoBuUwa_A">Tuế yến hành - 歲晏行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/T%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-li%C3%AAn-c%C3%BA-ng%C5%A9-ng%C3%B4n-b%C3%A0i-lu%E1%BA%ADt-nh%E1%BA%A5t-th%E1%BB%A7-h%E1%BA%A1n-nh%E1%BB%8B-ti%C3%AAu-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-wMQlYGlF6aUupM2pBicmdQ">Tức cảnh liên cú ngũ ngôn bài luật nhất thủ, hạn “nhị tiêu” vận - 即景聯句五言排律一首，限二蕭韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-C%C3%A1o/V%C4%83n-Ng%C3%B4-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-chinh-L%C4%A9nh-bi%E1%BB%83u-ti%C3%AAu-t%E1%BB%A9c/poem-ju6xJw-8wGLSQRAf5DU-uw">Văn Ngô Đức chinh Lĩnh biểu tiêu tức - 聞吳德征嶺表消息</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-C%C3%A1o/author-H9h3VFpWVHWoW69g54MirA">Trình Cáo</a>)<br></div>	</div>
